 prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAUiEwiP1s-QuOuTAxVQQ0IHHTSUM-hI-PzY5fOSkb2XAcoBBGuQ4og=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbHREYVlGQXNWdG5hQjlXOWpFU0RoQnpxV3VDQXxBQ3Jtc0ttR1BoSWE4Rk9TVU0xcU1sZHZrWHVNbzhsUExYYVRCQkFiM1l0TWlFTUNVcWhZQVhlUU9xbzlMM2ktTkFWMlJCamUyLVNZb0hCZ19WSHU5T01wdDA0VUc0T2N5VVNpWUdpU1RIZFlOU0pyUlNyX3pRTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=l3pElzy2Png","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbHREYVlGQXNWdG5hQjlXOWpFU0RoQnpxV3VDQXxBQ3Jtc0ttR1BoSWE4Rk9TVU0xcU1sZHZrWHVNbzhsUExYYVRCQkFiM1l0TWlFTUNVcWhZQVhlUU9xbzlMM2ktTkFWMlJCamUyLVNZb0hCZ19WSHU5T01wdDA0VUc0T2N5VVNpWUdpU1RIZFlOU0pyUlNyX3pRTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=l3pElzy2Png","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAUiEwiP1s-QuOuTAxVQQ0IHHTSUM-hI-PzY5fOSkb2XAcoBBGuQ4og=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbmRfMWdpdjVkcm9FajBtX2tWYjVUQzdIc1RMUXxBQ3Jtc0tuMXhpd0pWQ3JpNUhWU2N3QlozY29WYm1TUUhURTlEOUVEa2pZbG1pN2VPVmFjMF9fZVZaNjVsVENyX29YVU85TnQ4blVuY0sx